'''''Plan B''''' ni filime yo gusetsa y’urukundo ya [[Kenya]] na [[Nigeriya]] yasohotse 2019 <ref>https://nation.africa/kenya/life-and-style/showbiz/plan-b-a-hilarious-kenyan-love-tale-with-a-twist-138498</ref> yanditswe, iyobowe kandi ikosorwa nuwakoze firime ya Nigeriya, Lowladee. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo umukinnyi wa filime ukomoka muri Kenya akaba na producer Sarah Hassan, [[Catherine Kamau|Catherine Kamau Karanja]], hamwe n’umukinnyi wa [[Nigeriya]] Daniel Etim Effiong bakinnye. <ref name="B">https://paukwa.or.ke/plan-b/</ref> <ref name="P">https://www.bellanaija.com/2019/01/watch-trailer-for-lowladees-new-film-plan-b-on-bn/</ref>

Iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo '''cyiza cya Afurika y'Iburasirazuba''' muri Afurika ya Magic Viewers 'Choice Awards (AMVCAs). <ref>http://dx.doi.org/10.1163/1872-9037_afco_asc_3118</ref>

== Umusaruro ==
Iyi filime yakozwe na Lowladee ku bufatanye na Alfajiri Productions, uruganda rukora ibicuruzwa muri Kenya. <ref name="P" />

== Umugambi ==
Gutandukana na Ethan we (Lenana Kariba), Lisa Waweru ( Sarah Hassan ) yagiye kunywa mu kabari, ahahurira n'umugabo udasanzwe. Guhagarara ijoro rimwe hamwe n’umuntu utazi maze aratwita. Nyuma y'amezi atanu, umunyamurwango wacitse, Lisa, yamenye ko umugabo atwite ari umuyobozi mukuru wa Nigeriya muri Afrika yuburasirazuba akwirakwiza [[Nairobi|isosiyete ishingiye kuri Nairobi]], Dele Coker ( Daniel Etim Effiong ). Kuruhande rwinshuti ye, Joyce ( [[Catherine Kamau|Catherine Kamau Karanja]] ), gahunda nziza yageze kugirango Dele asabe inshingano zo gutwita. Iyi gahunda igomba rwose guhinduka ubuzima burambye kuri bose.  <ref>https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2019/02/plan-b.html</ref> <ref name="NTV">https://nation.africa/kenya/life-and-style/showbiz/plan-b-a-hilarious-kenyan-love-tale-with-a-twist-138498</ref> <ref>https://stories.showmax.com/7-nigerian-movies-you-can-enjoy-with-bae-in-february/</ref>

